data.name: btnContact.ToolTip
data.value:
Build Contact Details
Use this tab to create a set of contact
details that you can embed into a QR
Code.

This should create a new contact
on most mobile devices.

data.name: btnUrl.ToolTip
data.value:
Build URL
Use this tab to create a URL that can
be embedded into a QR Code.

This should open up the default
browser application on most
mobile devices.

data.name: btnSMS.ToolTip
data.value:
Build SMS
Use this tab to build an SMS message
that can be embedded into a QR Code.

NB: The phone number should not
include any spaces and be in the
following format +4420812341234

This should open up the default
sms messaging application on most
mobile devices.

data.name: btnEmail.ToolTip
data.value:
Build E Mail
Use this form to build an e mail
message that will be embedded
into the QR Code.

This should open up the default
e mail program on most mobile
devices.

data.name: btnPlainText.ToolTip
data.value:
Build Plain Text
Use this form to build a QR code
containing an arbitrary string.

This will cause most mobile devices
to load the string and take a default
action based on the string content.

data.name: lblIntro.Text
data.value:
1. Select the type of QR Code you wish to build.
  2. Once built click Create QR Code
  3. View QR Code Properties to see what effect changing certain properties has.
  4. Save the QR Code either as an image or copy text to clipboard to use elsewhere.
